{"tid":574905,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[導演介紹] 每個年代都有他的故事 Paul Thomas Anderson","createTime":"2018-02-27T20:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T01:28:55.000Z","uid":78390,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5c6ab8e8b9eda48c935d1768f2dd403e25a72c","tid":574905,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T20:55:16.000Z","msg":"可算係歐洲電影節可人兒<br />\n挑戰唔同時代題材同故事嘅導演<br />\n每一個成功嘅導演都有佢自己嘅風格<br />\nPaul Thomas Anderson(PTA) 就忠於小剪接加長鏡頭 令觀眾容易代入之如更帶來真實感<br />\n差唔多零失手而且繼續破舊立新<br />\n令觀眾每次期待下一部作品<br />\n<br />\n1890年至20世紀初<br />\nThere Will be Blood<br />\n第一次同Daniel Day Lewis合作<br />\n表演出野心同變得貪心嘅石油商人<br />\nPTA最勁係同邊個演員都能夠擦出唔同火花<br />\n寫嘅對白已經一流 加上堅持的長鏡頭小剪接<br />\n令觀眾更投入劇情<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045100_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045100_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3452fea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045111_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045111_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7ee7b370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n40年代至50年代<br />\nThe Master<br />\n關於Scientology嘅故事<br />\n主要圍繞一個當完兵嘅男人<br />\n返到黎失去了所有 與社會脱節<br />\n希望尋求别人同宗教拯救<br />\n算係本世紀拍得最靚嘅電影<br />\n加上Joaquin 超水準演出<br />\n都算十分完美嘅電影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045124_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045124_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bbecbf3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045135_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045135_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f159f2eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n60年代至70年代<br />\nInherent Vice<br />\n關於一個成日吸毒High 大咗嘅偵探故事 <br />\n呢部英文有啲難 所以唔係太明<br />\n不過再同Joaqin 合作<br />\n加上獲得唔少獎 值得一試<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045155_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045155_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82b5bd92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n80年代<br />\nBoogie Night<br />\n大家睇咁多AV 不如睇下呢套關於AV嘅電影<br />\n七八十年代最正一定係Disco 所以Soundtrack 一流<br />\n風格由呢部開始形成<br />\n長鏡頭一take過 對佢黎講無難度<br />\n加上PTA 寫嘅劇本 角色設計一流<br />\n真係一個唔錯嘅電影 不過就唔好同屋企人睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045209_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045209_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3809e900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045218_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045218_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7127fd4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n90年代<br />\nMagnolia<br />\n套戲三粒鐘 六個故事 零悶場<br />\n六個故事互相重疊交替 <br />\n大家的高低起伏其實可能符近都有人同你經歷<br />\n加上史上最經典嘅Twist 不過冇咩人記得<br />\n我認為係PTA最有心思嘅劇本<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045234_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045234_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d3e120d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045240_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045240_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1413fcd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n21世紀<br />\nPunch Drunk Love<br />\n呢套就九十分鐘 <br />\n一個孤獨而唔懂得表達自己嘅男人<br />\n遇到自己所愛<br />\n套戲當中的韻味 搞笑得黎又浪漫 捕捉得淋漓盡致<br />\n雖然冇PTA之前一貫作風 但一樣交到功課<br />\n抵你攞康城最佳導演<br />\n呢部溝囡一流<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045250_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045250_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b52a7838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045256_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045256_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=76db3983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPhantom Thread<br />\nPTA最新一部作品 第二次同Daniel Day Lewis聯手<br />\n今年都提名咗最佳電影同最佳導演<br />\n講一個服裝界大師遇上了佢愛嘅人<br />\n算係PTA最親民電影 搞笑而且<br />\n呢部戲會睇到目瞪口呆 透唔到氣嘅感覺<br />\n當中PTA對愛嘅睇法而且意想不到結局<br />\n完美配樂加服裝設計<br />\n都算一部頗完美嘅電影<br />\n求大家集氣希望佢可以攞最佳導演<br />\n不過照牌面都係Guillermo Del Toro架啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/045310_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F045310_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1b4c97b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"236ace22cfc15b87e6732a91df66e34b32f26044","tid":574905,"uid":42175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T21:09:08.000Z","msg":"未睇phantom thread<br />\n不過there will be blood入面ddl個演繹真係近十年數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e47fb38a076c2f926fe46b4ddf0d20d730e54f","tid":574905,"uid":85260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T21:54:53.000Z","msg":"Inherent vice睇住字幕都唔明佢up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f60d2ecfb8c8b2b47212dc736a28ad003af70c","tid":5